als that pass the protocol's rigorous criteria. Each report details a signa=
l's performance predicting stock returns using a wide array of tests and be=
nchmarks it to more than 200 other known anomalies. Finally, we use state-o=
f-the-art LLMs to generate three distinct complete versions of academic pap=
ers for each signal. The different versions include creative names for the =
signals, contain custom introductions providing different theoretical justi=
fications for the observed predictability patterns, and incorporate citatio=
